E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Tell this clipboard and earpiece motherfucker to back up, L. ~n~ -Back up!
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~－叫这个拿本子戴耳机的傻逼玩意让开，L。 ~n~－让开！

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Yes, you know, if the bodyguard/business partner thing doesn't work out,
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~确实。对了，如果保镖兼合伙人你干不了，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~And guess what? We ain't here about Gracie.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~没想到吧？我们不是为了Gracie来的。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~No more of that shit left, T.
~z~-Luis is my boy! ~n~ - Luis is his boy.
~z~Come on. I was kidding. The clubs fell apart without you.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~别啦，我开玩笑的。夜店没你就撑不住了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Yo relax, go inside, I got it.
~z~You trying to leave us behind? Get something we can all fit in.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你想把我们丢下吗？找辆三个人坐的下的车。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck are you talking about, man?
~z~Have it your way. See you soon.
~z~yeah, and you was holding court with that Cloe Parker until 4 am?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~然后你就跟那个Cloe Parker鬼混到4点？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~ - Enjoy looking for a job in this economic climate, motherfucker! ~n~ -Yeah!
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~－祝你在经济危机中顺利就业，傻逼玩意！~n~－就是！

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~One nightclub catering to the rich mindless crowd in a city where the rich mindless crowd are suddenly poor and mindless.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~一家店面向有钱无脑的庸人，而城里有钱无脑的庸人随时会没钱没脑。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~and maybe it's just hanging out with you - who the fuck knows?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~也可能是和你处太久了，这下说不清了。
~z~哇哦，市区真的让你变了，哥们。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I gotta make some calls. You work the floor.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我要打几个电话。你去楼下看看。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Okay, you just can't be looking like you came from selling dope on the corner.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~只是你们别打扮得跟在路边贩毒一样。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Luis - this is Vince and Rocco, relatives of Gracie.
~z~That the queen's car? You ain't gonna be his favorite piece of ass, bro.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~这是夜店女王的车？你肯定不是他最好的那个基友，兄弟。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Seven days. Junkies need junk rain, sleet, or shine.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~七天。瘾君子吸毒风雨无阻，不休息的。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Laters, L. Tell that boss of yours we'll be back same time next week.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~再会，L。告诉你老板我们下周这个点还来。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~they wanna stay up all night talking bullshit to morons because they enjoy it"
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~只要有白痴扎堆听他们吹逼到天亮，他们就高兴了。」

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Sometimes I wonder if you brought me on as a partner just to share the blame when the IRS comes knocking.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~有时候我都怀疑，你找我当合伙人是为了在国税局敲门的时候陪你背锅。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You see what I mean, L? They don't even have dishes at Burger Shot.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~这下懂我意思了没，L？吃得饱汉堡甚至连碗都没有。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~See you later. Oh, nice to meet you, muscles.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~二位再见。哦，很高兴见到你，肌肉男。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Nice boss you got there, stuck up fucking fag!
~z~Yeah, he says he saw you last night,
~z~They just about let me wash the god damn dishes.
~z~we're not spics, or guidos, or fags - we're proud Americans!
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我们不是西班牙佬，不是意大利佬，也不是死基佬——我们是骄傲的美国人！

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~IQ don't mean nothing, man. You guys are better than this. I don't want any of us to go away again.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~智商不能代表什么，伙计。你们没必要自甘堕落。我不想我们中再有人坐牢了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Oh, the usual. Boyfriend thinks I'm a cash machine.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~哦，日常了。男友当我是取款机。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I knew that club of yours was bullshit. You gonna take us back to the Heights or what?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道你们的夜店是坨屎。你要送我们回高地那边吗？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Shit. Troy. Let's find a doorman who isn't sexually repressed next time.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的。Troy。下回找个没有性压抑的门卫吧。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Anyway, uh- listen, I'm coming over. Okay? So wake up. You hear me? Wake up.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~总之，呃，听着，我过来了，好吗？该醒了。听见了吗？醒醒。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~That's what you say, T. Pero, I'm kind of suspicious. Maybe witnessing that robbery made me paranoid,
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~这能是真心话，T？我现在有点多疑。目击抢劫或许让我有被害妄想了，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You're too good to take money from me and Henrique now?
~z~Hey, Tony it's me. Yeah, there was a problem at the bank. Place got robbed.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Tony，是我。是，银行里出了点问题。那地方刚才被抢了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I love those people! And what's up with Dessie?
~z~A very important client is coming tonight. We need complete discretion.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~今晚有个很重要的客人要来，得做好万全准备。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~they must really really want to substitute my inadequacies with their money because, after all,
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~他们肯定非常非常地愿意，慷慨解囊来资助我，因为说到底，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Gentlemen, watch your language. We're in the great melting pot;
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~先生们，注意你们的用词。这里是一个大熔炉，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Fine men of the cloth. Who the fuck do you think they are?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~正人君子吗。这他妈还能是谁？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I was investing in your industry and acumen. Don't look for anything sinister here.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我只是看中了你的勤奋和敏锐，没别的不良动机。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~the girls all say they're fucking him,
~z~Alright, so take some time off, the girls in there could use a night off too.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~那好，休息一会吧，也让店里的女人休息一晚。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I don't know anything about it, but take care of it, Luis. No nonsense.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~什么都不知道，但请好好处理，Luis。别胡闹了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~and every half-wit, part time hood in the city thinking, "I know, let's put the squeeze on the club owners...
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~那些智障、半吊子的混混都想着「有了，干脆压榨夜店老板吧...

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Who the fuck were those two assholes, T?
~z~I don't care if you're his damn mother,
~z~That's good, because I am terrible. Fucking wretched.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~真好，因为我确实糟透了。巨他妈难受。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You sound like five-o. Shit. You think Henrique could get a job at Burger Shot?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你丫是条子吗。妈的。你觉得Henrique会被吃得饱聘用吗？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I don't want it in the bank!
~z~Work them corners, man. Work them corners.
~z~Yeah, I had a complicated day, okay?
~z~when the gay and decadent crowd suddenly think decadence means buying outrageous new throw cushions
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~而纸醉金迷的基佬突然觉得，纸醉金迷需要的是买新得要命的抱枕，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Ancelotti goons I borrowed money from way back...never mind.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~Ancelotti的打手，我很久之前问他们借过钱...别管了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Before you went in there you was a skinny little shit and now you pumped up.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~进去之前，你就是一细竹竿，现在壮得一逼。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~He's paranoid no one will buy his next CD if they know he'd rather be singing cabaret than rapping.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~他就怕没人买他的新CD，不想被人知道他更愿意唱卡巴莱而不是搞说唱。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~instead of getting loaded in a bar,
~z~I love getting racially abused by a spic.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~哦，西班牙佬都敢玩种族歧视了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Don't tell me you been running a skim job.
~z~I'm one hundred percent legitimate, Luis. You know me. Total transparency.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我可是实打实的守法公民，Luis。你了解我的。一清二白。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You ain't no postman, Loco, you're a pusher. All those hours.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你又不是邮差，疯子，你是个毒贩子。有这个时间，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You don't get no pussy working Burger Shot neither.
~z~You ain't gonna fit both me and Rique in there. Get something bigger.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~这车我和Rique只能上一个。找辆大点的。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I should be sent to prison. Shouldn't I?
~z~I'm told that one of your "friends" is causing trouble out front. Can you go help Dessie?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~听说你的「朋友」在门口闹事。你能不能去帮帮Dessie？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, we have a no guido policy at the club; here I ain't so sure.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~对，夜店那边是意大利佬勿入，这边就不确定了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I took a bid for you once, man. I ain't going back there. You think I put in all this work to go back inside?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我替你们进去过一次了，伙计，才不要再回去。你以为我这么努力是为了回去坐牢？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Hello. Hey mami, como esta? Yeah, I'm sorry, yeah- no, I was working late at the club. Yeah.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你好。嘿，老妈，近况如何？是，我很抱歉，对-不，我只是在夜店工作到很晚。是。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~is that people know better what their vagina looks like than their face.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~比他们的脸都要出名几百倍。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~man, it's easier to get into your apartment than into your nightclub.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~真是，进你家都比进你的店容易。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~There ain't another job in the city for this dumb bastard to do; hourly wage considered, and all.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~城里再找不出这种白痴弱智能做的了，连时薪制的都没有。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck is wrong with you, man?
~z~Another club catering to the gay and decadent crowd
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~还有一家面向纸醉金迷的基佬，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Mami, don't be like that. Okay? I'll come home soon. Look, I got to go. Okay, bye.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~老妈，别这样。好吗？我最近会回趟家的。那个，我得挂了。好的，再见。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Amateurs. Come on, let's get out of here, let's go.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~俩业余的。来吧，我们出去吧，走。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Oh yeah, thank you so much, man.
~z~Come to think of it Lou, what the fuck are you wearing, huh?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~说起衣服，Lou，你丫身上这又是啥，啊？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Your connections, man, we'll have the whole city on our gear.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~有你的人脉，兄弟，整座城市都是我们的囊中之物。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Dessie wouldn't let me in dressed like that.
~z~Yo, why you laying your hands on me like that, man?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~哟，你怎么对我动手动脚的，伙计？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Oh, man, Armando? Shit. What am I gonna do now?
~z~You'd make more slinging meat at Burger Shot than risking a bid on them corners.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~去吃得饱做汉堡肉都比冒风险贩毒好。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Nothing to do with me. I swear. Um, some Irish guys.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~和我没关系。我发誓。呃，几个爱尔兰人。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Jesus, Dessie. Who would have thought running the door here was such a dangerous gig.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~妈呀，Dessie。谁能想到在这看门是这么危险的活。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, it's me, Tone. Things go smooth at the clubs?
~z~-That's a start. I guess we don't have to beat you two lovers up. ~n~ -Good one!
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~－这样就好。看来这下不用棒打鸳鸯了。 ~n~－说得好！

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I don't know - I think the little people who live in his head, the ones stuck in 1955?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~不知道，可能是他脑子里住着的小人吧？现在还活在1955年。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~ Tony, I just went to the bank for you, man...
~z~Don't tell me that sugar daddy of yours woulda been interested in the scrawny fucker that went away?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~别跟我说你干爹会喜欢进去前那种皮包骨头的细竹竿？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~-Yeah, go relax, go inside, huh? ~n~-Call your mami!
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~－对，去放松，进去吧，啊？ ~n~－找你妈去吧！

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Have it your way. See you soon.
~z~I never thought about being grateful to you for signing me up to the "fight off hairy ass rapists day and night" exercise plan.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我还真没为被你们送进「日夜打退多毛傻逼鸡奸犯」的健身课说过谢谢。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Made me wonder why I need you around at all.
~z~Forty-five years old and I get my kicks doing blow with seventeen year old kids whose only claim to fame
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~都45岁了，还跟17岁的小孩口到爽翻天，然而他们的逼

E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~得了得了得了。下次再说，Troy。我们要去豪宅了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Oye, A! I've been thinking about this: How many days a week you work those corners?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，A！我一直在想：你一周有几天在贩毒？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, L. You gave it to them! I knew this downtown bullshit would get to you.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，L。你屈服于他们了！我就知道市中心的狗屁会影响你。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You say that like it's a bad thing.
~z~Give it up, Tone. Where'd the cash come from?
~z~All that money on helicopter lessons and you don't even know how to drive? Great.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~花了那么多钱学直升机，结果你连车都不会开？真好。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You know me, Tone. Don't ask, don't tell. Military grade.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你了解我的，Tone。不会问，不用说。军规级的。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~The nightclub business is going to shit. Forget the banks, we're the ones who needed a bailout.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~夜店生意一团糟。别救银行了，我们才需要政府拨款。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Half the people in here say Luis is their boy;
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~店里至少一半人跟Luis称兄道弟，

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~What's wrong with you, back on the roids? We got a business to run, you idiot Luis.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你咋回事，又开始用类固醇了？我们有生意要做，白痴Luis。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~If you do nothing else, put on some clothes, huh?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~没别的事做，就换身衣服，好吧？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Prison was the best thing to happen to you, L.
~z~What they gonna let you do at Burger Shot with an IQ sub eighty?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~智商没上80的人在吃得饱能干啥？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Come on board with us. We can start selling our own product.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~跟我们合作吧。我们可以开始卖自己的货。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Not with the way police treat an ex-con in this town.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~光看这里的警察怎么对待前科犯就不需要。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, he said he loves you, but he can't handle working the door of a gay club anymore. Says people are laughing at him.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~嗯，他说他爱你，但他不想给男同夜店看门了。说是有人笑话他。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Saw that bank robbery on the news. Could have been an opportunity for some positive PR.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我在新闻上看到银行劫案了。本来你可以搞点正面公关的。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~I'm good, boss. How are you? You look terrible.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~我很好，老板。你怎么样？看起来糟透了。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Sure. Look. I really need to talk to you, Tony.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~确实。那个，我们真的要好好谈谈，Tony。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~you should consider a career as a fucking life coach.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~你应该考虑去当个什么人生导师。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~Oh great. I might just take a vacation then.
~z~Fuck that shit. I don't need any press like that.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~去他妈的。我不需要这种报道。

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~If them Ivy League motherfuckers can't find work, what you think Rique is meant to do?
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~如果连名校毕业的傻逼玩意都找不到工作，你觉得Rique能干什么？

E2T1AUD.original: ~z~You know it ain't even like that, bro, okay? You don't pay for shit in here.
E2T1AUD.translated: ~z~情况不是这样的，懂吧？进去了免单都行。
